title: DISNEYS-TREASURE ISLAND[1950]-H.264 BY STIG
description:
In this swashbuckling, high-seas adventure, Walt Disney has vividly brought to life Robert Louis Stevenson's thrilling tale of buccaneers and buried gold - presented for the first time in it's original, uncut, theatrical version! Authentic locales and musket-roaring action set the stage for the stouthearted heroics of young Jim Hawkins (Bobby Driscoll) and the skullduggery of that wily, one-legged pirate, Long John Silver.
